Programming Language Used -> Java

How to run :-

1) Run the make file.
2) Run ./participate.sh <host_name/host_ip> <port_number> (Run it for all participants).
3) Run ./coordinator.sh <port_number> participants.txt
4) Run ./client.sh operations1.txt


Sample Input/Output

1) Participant

chetan@chetan-Lenovo-Yoga-3-14:~/eclipse_workspace/Two_Phase_Commit_1st_Copy$ ./participant.sh localhost 8081
